! Asphere-parameter modifiers: variables (AC..IC var codes), pickups
! (PIK K/A..I), save/reload round-trip, and optimization via a coefficient.
!
! 1) Pickups: S4 mirrors S1's conic and A4 (PIK K / PIK A), including after
!    a post-reload edit of the source surface (proves the pickup stays live).
RES OsdAsDoublet
ASP S1
ASP S4
K S1 -0.5
A S1 1.0e-5
PIK K S4 S1
PIK A S4 S1
SUR SA
LIS
SAV asphmod
RES asphmod
K S1 -0.9
A S1 3.0e-5
LIS
! 2) Variable codes: AC/KC round-trip through save (merit block) and display.
AC S1 0
KC S1 0
SAV asphmod
RES asphmod
! 3) Optimization: singlet with SAS=0 constraint driven by the A4 coefficient
! (proves the optimizer actually varies an asphere coefficient).
LEN NEW
EPD 20.0
THI S1 6.0
GLA S1 BK7
STO S1
INS S2
RDY S2 -10.0
ASP S2
PIM
SI 0.0 0.0
AC S2 0
AUT
SAS = 0
GO
LIS
